=You are enriching discovery data for semantic search. Use ONLY the provided inputs below.

INPUTS:
- Title: {{ $('Handle Photo Upload').item.json.title }}
- Description: {{ $('Handle Photo Upload').item.json.description }}
- Category: {{ $('Handle Photo Upload').item.json.type }}
- Address: {{ $('Handle Photo Upload').item.json.address || 'none' }}
- URL: {{ $('Handle Photo Upload').item.json.url || 'none' }}

CRITICAL: The enriched description MUST be based on the title "{{ $('Handle Photo Upload').item.json.title }}" and description "{{ $('Handle Photo Upload').item.json.description }}" above. Do not invent unrelated content.

TASK:
Generate a JSON response with:
{
  "enriched_description": "<expand the provided description with relevant context, max 80 words>",
  "keywords": ["<5-8 relevant keywords based on the category and description>"]
}

Keyword examples by category:
- For medical/healthcare: ["healthcare", "medical", "specialist", "clinic", "doctor", location]
- For coffee shops: ["coffee", "cafe", "wifi", "atmosphere", location]
- For restaurants: ["food", "dining", "cuisine", "restaurant", location]

Return ONLY valid JSON with no explanation or markdown formatting.

